      "content": "<p>Very late, but finally got a look at UzB. </p><p>Very easy win, and probably here also CR7 will score a few goals.</p><p>Portugal had to settle for a 1–1 draw against the Democratic Republic of the Congo in its opening match. The result was one of the biggest surprises of the opening round, and it could hardly be considered unjust, as Portugal's status as the favorite was reflected more in name than in the actual chances created. The underwhelming performance further raises questions about Cristiano Ronaldo’s role in terms of the team’s attacking output.</p><p>Uzbekistan, meanwhile, suffered a 1–3 defeat to Colombia in its opening fixture. The final score largely matched pre-match expectations, but the team showed that it can, at least in spells, challenge stronger opponents while in possession. Fabio Cannavaro’s side already had only the slimmest hopes of reaching the knockout stage, and picking up points in its final two group matches appears unlikely.</p><p>Portugal’s performance in the opening round fell well short of expectations, but creating chances against Uzbekistan should be considerably easier, both in open play and from set pieces. The gap in squad quality between the two teams is significant, and even if Uzbekistan manages to defend resolutely for periods, Portugal’s superior individual talent should be enough to secure victory for the Lusitanians with roughly an 80% probability.</p><br/><br/><b>该文章通过有道机器翻译，仅供参考:</b><br/><br/><p>很晚了，但终于看到了UzB。 </p>\n<p>很容易取胜，也许CR7也会进几个球。</p>\n<p>葡萄牙队在首场比赛中只得1-1战平刚果民主共和国。这一结果是首轮最大的意外之一，很难被认为是不公平的，因为葡萄牙的热门地位更多地反映在名义上，而不是实际创造的机会。这种平淡无奇的表现进一步引发了人们对c罗在球队进攻端的作用的质疑。</p>\n<p>与此同时，乌兹别克斯坦在首场比赛中以1-3不敌哥伦比亚。最终的比分基本上符合赛前的预期，但这支球队表明，至少在魔咒中，他们可以在控球时挑战更强大的对手。法比奥·卡纳瓦罗的球队进入淘汰赛阶段的希望已经非常渺茫，在最后两场小组赛中拿分似乎不太可能了。</p>\n<p>葡萄牙在首场比赛中的表现远远低于预期，但在对阵乌兹别克斯坦的比赛中创造机会应该要容易得多，无论是在空挡还是定位球中。两队之间的阵容差距很大，即使乌兹别克斯坦在一段时间内成功防守，葡萄牙出色的个人天赋也足以确保卢西塔尼亚人以大约80%的概率获胜。</p>",
